stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: HUD.show()
    Created --> Showing: Animation In
    Showing --> Updating: Update progress/label
    Updating --> Showing: Continue
    Showing --> Hiding: hud.hide() / auto-dismiss
    Hiding --> Hidden: Animation Out
    Hidden --> [*]: Removed from superview

    Showing --> Showing: Timer reset
    Hiding --> Callback: completionBlock / delegate
    Callback --> Hidden
